content: On master, there are a number of items listed as stabilized in 1.53 that were actually stabilized in 1.52. I haven't checked them all, but the inherent char methods/consts all seem to be wrongly duplicated.
I think that's because the relnotes label was added when we were on 1.53: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/82919#event-4621313058
No problem. Was updating standback and thought some of the items looked familiar. It happens!
